Module mesakit.graph.core
Package com.telenav.mesakit.graph.specifications.library.attributes

Interface AttributeStore

All Superinterfaces:
com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.naming.NamedObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
ArchivedGraphElementStore, EdgeStore, GraphElementStore, NodeStore, OsmEdgeStore, PlaceStore, RelationStore, ShapePointStore, VertexStore
public interface AttributeStore extends com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.naming.NamedObject
A store of attributes which is loaded with an AttributeLoader. Examples of attribute stores are all of the subclasses of GraphElementStore, such as VertexStore and EdgeStore An attribute store has an owning graph and a count of attributes.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
See Also:
GraphElementStore, Graph, AttributeLoader, AttributeReference
